AFN LOOPLESS BULLBAR TO SUIT SUZUKI JIMNY (2019)

AFN loopless bullbar to suit Suzuki Jimny (2019) available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

The pictured bullbar features;

  • Full bumper replacement
  • Dual Antenna Tabs
  • Winch Compatible
  • Hi-lift Jack points
  • Utilitses OEM Fog light – Includes new AFN LED indicator/DRL Light Assemblies
  • Ace Black Powder Coated supplied as standard

PLEASE NOTE: Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order. 

To view the range of products available for your Suzuki Jimny, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
